    <p><anchor n="T.50.2059.0416c07"/><lb ed="T" n="0416c07"/><persName key="A003526">釋道儒</persName>，姓石，<placeName key="PL000000003155">渤海</placeName>人。寓居<placeName key="PL000000010835">廣陵</placeName>。少懷清信，<lb ed="T" n="0416c08"/>慕樂出家。遇<persName key="A002151">宋臨川王義慶</persName>鎮<placeName key="PL000000010833">南兗</placeName>，<persName key="A003526">儒</persName>以<lb ed="T" n="0416c09"/>事聞之。<persName key="A002151">王</persName><ptr target="fn19"/>贊成厥志，為啟度出家。出家<lb ed="T" n="0416c10"/>之後，蔬食讀誦，凡所之造，皆勸人改惡修<lb ed="T" n="0416c11"/>善，遠近宗奉，遂成導師。言無預撰，發<ptr target="fn20"/>嚮<lb ed="T" n="0416c12"/>成製。<date key="j18854211886925" notAfter-iso="0454-02-14" notBefore-iso="0450">元嘉末</date>出<placeName key="PL000000008976">都</placeName>，止<placeName key="PL000000008825">建初寺</placeName>。<persName key="A003527">長沙王</persName>請為<lb ed="T" n="0416c13"/>戒師，<persName key="A003528">廬<ptr target="fn21"/>承相</persName>、<persName key="A003529">伯仲孫</persName>等共買<persName key="A003530">張敬兒</persName>故<ptr target="fn22"/>廟，<lb ed="T" n="0416c14"/>為<persName key="A003526">儒</persName>立寺，今<placeName key="PL000000008650">齊福寺</placeName>是也。<persName key="A003526">儒</persName>以<date key="j19000671900420" from-iso="0490-02-07" to-iso="0491-01-26">齊永明八<lb ed="T" n="0416c15"/>年</date>卒，年八十一。</p><p><ptr target="fn23"/>時<placeName key="PL000000008710">閑心寺</placeName>有<persName key="A003531">釋僧喜</persName>，亦<lb ed="T" n="0416c16"/><ptr target="fn24"/>善唱說，振譽於宋<ptr target="fn25"/>末齊初。</p>
